        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 26 at 7:17PM MDT until July 26 at 8:00PM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>SVRGGW

The National Weather Service in Glasgow has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
North central Phillips County in northeastern Montana...

* Until 800 PM MDT.

* At 716 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Turner, or 31
miles west of Whitewater, moving southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Hail damage to vehicles is expected. Expect wind damage
to roofs, siding, and trees.

* Locations impacted include...
Loring, Port Of Morgan, and Chapman.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
